Build a form validation flow

- first name (required, min 3 chars)
- last name (required, min 3 chars)
- email (required, must be valid format)
- password (required, min 6 chars)

Requiredments:
- validations hould happen as the user types
- submit button should only be enabled when all fields are valid
- provide visual feedback (e.g. red border for error, green checkmark for valid)
- vanilla js or react
